Introduction

BLINGONE China is the second unit of BLINGONE under World K-pop Center. They were formed by the audition Click The Star China. BLINGONE China is preceded by BLINGONE-PE. The group consists of 6 members: Sandy, Ranee, Katrina, Cassie, Junny, and Chloe. They debuted in February 13, 2025 with the single album “BubbleGum”
